    <section>
      <title>Introduction</title>
      <p>This page describes the requirements and identifies the many options for running <strong>Barcode4J</strong>.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <title>Requirements</title>
      <ul>
        <li>Java Runtime Environment (JRE) 1.4 or higher (available from <jump href="http://java.com/en/download/manual.jsp">java.com</jump>)</li>
        <li>Download <strong>Barcode4J</strong> as described on:</li>
        <ul>
          <li>the <link href="../download.html">Download page</link>, or</li>
          <li>from <link href="../viewcvs.html">CVS</link> (requires <jump href="ext:ant.apache.org">Apache Ant</jump> 1.6.2 or higher, then follow directions on the <link href="building.html">Building page</link>)</li>
        </ul>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
      <title>Running</title>
      <p>Depending on how you will run <strong>Barcode4J</strong>, you will have differing dependencies. Click the links below for directions on using <strong>Barcode4J</strong>:</p>
