        <li><link href="xalan-ext.html">...with Apache Xalan-J</link></li>
        <li><link href="saxon-ext.html">...with SAXON</link></li>
        <li><link href="fop-ext.html">...with Apache FOP</link></li>
        <li><link href="servlet.html">...in a Servlet</link></li>
        <li><link href="cli.html">...from the Command Line</link></li>
        <li><link href="embedding.html">...embedding in a Java application</link></li>
        <li><link href="embedding-bean.html">...embedding in Java (Bean API)</link></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
